reviewText: My 2 y o loves this DVD
My daughter loves this DVD! She is two years old and knows a few Russian words. It's awesome!

I am Russian but we only speak English at home.  I bought this thinking it would be a cute way for both my son and my husband to learn some words.  It's a cute little video.  Not something my pre-schooler will watch over and over again, but a fun little change.
